        <p><strong>Zone — Western Suburbs</strong><br>St Albans, Keilor, Keilor East, Keilor Downs, Keilor Lodge, Keilor Park, Sydenham, Taylors Lakes, Taylors Hill, Caroline Springs, Burnside, Burnside Heights, Melton, Melton South, Melton West, Diggers Rest, Rockbank, Cobblebank, Bacchus Marsh, Ravenhall, Cairnlea, Kealba, Kings Park, Delahey, Hillside, Calder Park, Plumpton, Fraser Rise, Aintree, Deanside, Mount Cottrell</p>

        <h2>Delivery & Ordering</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Order by cut-off time for next-day delivery</li>
          <li>Melbourne metro only</li>
          <li>No subscription required</li>
          <li>Direct to your door</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Common Delivery Questions</h2>
        <p><strong>Where does GrowDirect deliver?</strong><br>GrowDirect currently focuses on selected Melbourne metro suburbs across 8 active delivery zones.</p>
        <p><strong>How do I know if my suburb is included?</strong><br>Check the zone lists above to confirm your suburb is within the active delivery area before shopping.</p>
